menu "Aliro reader"

    config WOZ_ALIRO_LAB
        bool "Aliro Lab transaction trace"
        default y
        help
            Compile in the structured "[ALAB] t=<us> ev=..." trace at transaction
            phase boundaries (connect, auth, ranging setup, first range, bolt) so
            tools/aliro_lab.py can turn a captured serial log into a scored
            walk-up report. Like the sibling `uwbdiag` trace, it ships in every
            Aliro build but stays OFF at boot — the `lab on`/`lab off` console
            command toggles it at runtime, off the UWB hot path. Set n to strip
            it entirely from a hardened production image.

endmenu
